<facsimile><graphic url="https://www.e-manuscripta.ch/i3f/v20/1079487/manifest"/></facsimile><text><body><div type="letter">
<pb facs="1079488" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Illustrissimo atque Celeberrimo Viro <choice><abbr>Jo.</abbr><expan>Johanni</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> Petrus Antonius <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelottus</rs></salute></opener>
  <p>Quam gratissimae mihi fuerint humanissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> doctissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que <rs key="B_1724-05-31_991170515107705501" type="letter">lite<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>r<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tu[a]e</rs>, Vir Sapientissime, Pridie Kalendas Junias isth<choice><orig><g ref="#ihat">î</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>c
    <lb/>datis, verbis declarare non possum. Jis, uti et compluribus
    <lb/>aliis, quibus alias me cumulasti beneficiis, me Tibi, Tuis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que omnibus, et praesertim ingeniosissimo, suavissimoque
    <lb/>Filio Tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Danieli</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ternum devinxisti. Responsionem
    <lb/>quemadmodum Tu hortatus es, ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Jurinianam</rs> <rs key="biblio_42TNNPE9" type="biblio">De<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>fensionem</rs> post quindecim aut 20 dies edere curabo simul
    <lb/>cum illa ipsa <rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Juriniana</rs> <rs key="biblio_42TNNPE9" type="biblio">Defensione</rs>, inde et ad Te, et
    <lb/>ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtonum</rs>, et <rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Jurinum</rs> in <rs key="place_VER-englan" type="place">Angliam</rs>, et ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-118639056" type="person">Fontenellum</rs>,
    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-11931035X" type="person">Mairanum</rs>, aliosque in <rs key="place_VER-frankr" type="place">Gallia</rs> data occasione me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>Responsionis exemplaria aliquot simul cum <choice><abbr>Cl.</abbr><expan>Clarissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filii</rs>
    <lb/>Tui a me dilectissimi <rs key="biblio_WZBB3ZSY" type="biblio">Controversiis</rs><note type="editorial">Michelotti könnte sich hier auf das vermutlich gerade im Druck befindliche Werk Daniel I. B.'s beziehen: St.4 Exercitationes quaedam mathematicae, Venetiis: Apud Dominicum Lovisam, 1724 - Werke 1, pp.297-362.</note> propediem prodituris
    <lb/>transmittam. Mihi plane omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mecum <rs key="B_1724-05-31_991170515107705501" type="letter">suprame<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>moratis Tuis litteris</rs> communicasti, mihi omnino, in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quam satisfaciunt. Recte facis mathematicis studiis,
    <lb/>omnique litterarum commercio {*}<!-- Warum hier der Stern in geschweiften klammern? --> valedicendo tuend<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> valetudinis, quam secundam per longissimam
    <lb/>annorum seriem Tibi exopto, causa. Nihilo tamen secius
    <lb/>non orare Te non possum, ut una adhuc tantum
    <lb/>vice quambrevissima epistola mihi explanes
    <lb/>sequentem difficultatem circa vim aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per foramen vasis
    <lb/>alicuius effluentis motum generantem. Hac enim difficul<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tate mihi amota nullus amplius circa hanc rem mihi su<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pererit scrupulus. Aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> partes laterales statim ac
    <lb/>aqua per foramen erumpere incipit nonne confluunt
         <pb facs="1079489" n="2"/>
    <lb/>ubique horizontaliter, et fortasse etiam oblique a lateri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus vasis, nonne, inquam, simul influunt in columnam
    <lb/>aqueam foramini vasis perpendiculariter imminentem?
    <lb/>Si igitur confluunt ejusmodi partes aquae laterales, moti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus suis augere poterunt vim pressionis cylindric<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> aque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, foramini ad perpendiculum insisten<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tis, seu pressionem columnarum obliquarum <add><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que ac</add> illa
    <lb/>colummna perpendicularis ponderantium. Ita, in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quam, augere poterunt vim pressionis aque<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> colum<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>n<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> perpendicularis ut hujus pressio ita
    <lb/>aucta <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis sit pressioni dupli ponderis cy<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lindric<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> foramini vasis ad perpendicu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lum insistentis. Partes aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> laterales moveri atque
    <lb/>in cylindricam columnam perpendiculariter foramini
    <lb/>insistentem influere, ipse quoque falsus est, quem
    <lb/>admodum colligere poteris ex iis, quae olim
    <lb/>mecum communicasti, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que legere poteris in
    <lb/>mea <rs key="biblio_M3G2JA79" type="biblio">Dissertatione</rs><note type="editorial">Michelotti, Pietro Antonio, De separatione fluidorum in corpore animali dissertatio physico-mechanico-medica, Venetiis (A. &amp; A. Pinelli) 1721. (Digitalisat bei BSB digital  https://books.google.ch/books?id=tzKwrr4zbx8C&amp;pg=PA30&amp;lpg=PA30&amp;dq=dissertatio+de+separatione+fluidorum&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=gYZ1FDnvRP&amp;sig=ACfU3U1tida-DJga5qbTGPHdYS6u0yNJEw&amp;hl=de&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiq9fu51p_hAhXL1uAKHV4rB5IQ6AEwC3oECAcQAQ#v=onepage&amp;q=dissertatio%20de%20separatione%20fluidorum&amp;f=false), S. 128 Mitte.</note> de Separatione Fluidorum
    <lb/>pag. 128. Jbi enim, Te consentiente scripsi: <hi rend="u">Deinde
      <lb/>aquam in partibus <formula>M</formula>,<formula>R</formula>, existentem revera sese move<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re, atque spatium <formula>SECCES</formula> influere ad perturbandum
  <lb/>motum aquae delabentis per istam commentitiam
      <lb/>Cataractam <formula>SECCES</formula>, probat sequens experimentum.</hi>
</p>
<p>Ut super hac re quamcitissime per <rs key="place_GEO-2775220" type="place">Oenipontum</rs>
  <lb/>fieri poterit ad me quid Tibi videatur scribas
  <lb/>pro sola hac vice etiam atque etiam quaeso,
  <lb/>et oro. Exhortor assidue <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Ornatissimum Filium
             <pb facs="1079490" n="3"/>
    <lb/>Tuum</rs>, quem loco Filii semper habebo, ut mecum
  <lb/>practicam Medicinam omnibus aliis studiis relictis
  <lb/>excolat. Ipse se id quamprimum facturum summa
  <lb/>cum animi attentione sancte pollicitus est mihi.</p>
<closer><salute>Vale,
  <lb/>Celeberrime Amicissimeque Vir, Vale, inquam, plurimum,
  <lb/>mihique, quod facis, favere perge.</salute>
<dateline><choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Dabam</expan></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> Pridie
  <lb/>Kalendas Julias 1724.</dateline>
